name: The cave
description: I am in a strange place, it looks like a cave, but what is this portal, why is it blinking? Should I go there? I have a very strange feeling, the air is so heavy and it smells damp here, it doesn't seem like there would be someone here ... it's too quiet here. A feeling of fear envelops me and it seems to me the most reasonable way out would be to enter this portal. It seems to me that he is call me... i enter
